AUDIO: 'We have a new state-of-the-art open source model that can create 4K resolution images. Not only is this really detailed, but it\'s also incredibly fast and lightweight. I can generate an image in less than 5 seconds. This is called Pixel Diffusion or PID for short, and this is by Nvidia.'

[00:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
